title: PS Brush set #3 - Light Effects Brushes ~ Diva of Design
description:
Here is my third brush collection for Photoshop. Should work just fine in all versions of the program, and if you need help or not sure how to install brushes feel free to send me a PM. ~ DH

These are my most used brushes in all of my designs. I use them in each, and every image. They add amazing high quality lighting effects and are very simple to use! Also included in the set are the original stock images of the sun flares the brushes were made out of...
